{"id":603144896,"lang":"cpp","lang_name":"C++","time":"1 year, 8 months","timestamp":1639745876,"status":10,"status_display":"Accepted","runtime":"31 ms","url":"/submissions/detail/603144896/","is_pending":"Not Pending","title":"Longest Substring Without Repeating Characters","memory":"8.3 MB","code":"class Solution {\npublic:\n    \n    int lengthOfLongestSubstring(string s) {\n        int n = s.size();\n        unordered_map<char,int> set;\n        int m = 0;\n        int i = 0;\n        for(int j = 0; j < n; ++j){\n            if(set.count(s[j])){\n                i = max(i, set[s[j]]+1);\n            }\n            set[s[j]] = j;\n            m = max(m, j-i+1);\n        }\n        return m;\n    }\n};","compare_result":"","title_slug":"longest-substring-without-repeating-characters","has_notes":false,"flag_type":1}
